{
  "stem": "11611.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It is Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Karl Rasche of the Dresdner Bank.' That sounded good to me too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I liked that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It had the right flavor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then we had this huge aryanization report.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Deutsche Bank, under Abs, had done exactly the same things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Abs?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No question, Abs, and we would have indicted Abs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead, Abs went on to become either a cabinet member under Adenauer, or very close to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a very prominent German banker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ultimate German banker in the post-war period, with, as I say, great connections to Lehman Brothers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He put out a book on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, because we were down to one man, and an SS colonel was better than a Nazi party member, and we had this aryanization report.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was part of the selection as to which way we went and Rasche was my choice.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got the Rasche case exclusively and became a trial team all by myself, right out of the law school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I was part of the ministry's case, which was a big catch-all case.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really a last case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was case number 11 of 12, but 12, I think, was almost over by the time this one was formed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then after awhile, they added another defendant for me in the form of Emil Puhl who was a vice president of the Reichsbank.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The president had been acquitted in the big trial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was shocked, but I got the vice president.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they added still another defendant who was Hans Kehrl, who was undersecretary of the Ministry of Economics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were all my defendants exclusively.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had a pretty good role.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
